snippet.title: Them's Fightin' Herds - 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The 1.0 release of indie fighting game "Them's Fightin' Herds" is available now on PC, which includes the first chapter of story mode!

Purchase your Steam key from the Humble Bundle Store:
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/thems-fightin-herds

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/tfh
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ManeSix
